{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "缪文乘白马银车赴杭州，途中遇两匹明驼和塞外丽人，乱发头陀追踪而去。车至偃月清池，程七发现江南地面竟有蒙古包；黄衣童子柳儿与蒙装少女桃姑以主人相邀，将缪文引入富丽帐中。蒙面老人先礼后试，以高妙乌光暗器逼探其胆气，又命桃姑、柳儿挖眼。缪文为免泄露化骨神拳强忍杀机，危急时华山银鹤挥银剑闯入解围，并指老人一行似塞上温柔阱。乱发头陀随后破帐而入，见老人后大受震动，老人最终扯下面巾，竟是八面玲珑胡之辉。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "乱发头陀",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "杭州城见。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qi",
      "speaker_name": "快马程七",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "公子，你看这里。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cheng_qi",
      "speaker_name": "快马程七",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "奇怪，江南地面，怎会有那塞外的'蒙古包'布在这里？\n我向来只闻得有'塞外江南'，想不到今日竟看到了江南的塞外风物。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_er",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣童子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "水上一鹭飞，池底万鱼惊……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gu",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面少女",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "对面的客人，请你下车来好么？\n我们的主人请你帐篷里坐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_er",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣童子",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "好漂亮的马！\n好漂亮的马车！好漂亮的人！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_liu_er",
      "text": "小弟弟，你们的主人是谁？\n唤我作什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_er",
      "speaker_name": "黄衣童子",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "我也不知道，也许他认识你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gu",
      "speaker_name": "桃姑",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "老爷子，客人过来了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "外面的客人快请进来，恕老夫行走不便，有失远迎。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gu",
      "speaker_name": "桃姑",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "老爷子请你进来。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "兄台只管随意坐吧，请恕老夫无礼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "在下缪文，蒙老丈宠召，不知有何见教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_tao_gu",
      "text": "坐，坐……桃姑，茶来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "兄台人中之龙，举止非凡，不知是哪位贤父母，方自生得出如此佳弟子？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "家父母俱是凡人，经商粤东，看老丈方是人中之龙，飘忽来去，却不知来到江南，有何贵干？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "在下虽然……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "好武功呀好武功，好胆气呀好胆气，老夫双眼不盲，兄台若是高人弟子，老夫便也是弟子高人了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "老丈过奖了，在下有什么武功，有什么胆气，不过深信老丈与在下无冤无仇，绝不至要取我之性命，是以才还稳得住，何况——哈哈。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "在下便是心中要想闪避，却也不知该如何闪避呢？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "你明知老夫不会伤你性命，你才不避不闪是么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "在下与老丈素不相识，老丈唤我前来，如此戏弄，目的究竟是什么？\n倒叫在下费解。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "桃姑，柳儿，你两人一人去为老夫挖下此人的一只眼珠。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_gu",
      "speaker_name": "桃姑",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "客人真对不起你了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "speaker_name": "帐外来人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "text": "阁下是否华山门下，为何到此撒野？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍道人",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "我听闻玉门关外，有一伙独行大盗，杀人越货，无所不为，久走沙漠的行旅，都将之唤做'塞上温柔阱'。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍道人",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "沙漠上饥渴的旅人，只要遇上这'塞上温柔阱'，必定尸骨无存，想不到这'塞上温柔阱'，今日居然到了江南——哼哼，难道沙漠上的旅人，都已被你们害光了么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "text": "你说什么？当真可笑得很。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "speaker_name": "灰袍道人",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "塞上温柔阱以绝色美女，阵阵肉香，来引诱沙漠上的旅人，进入他们的帐篷，然后再加残杀，这行径正与你同出一辙，卖傻作甚？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "speaker_name": "华山银鹤",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "只是你这'塞上温柔阱'今日撞到了我'华山银鹤'手里，只怕你自今而后，再也无法害人了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "text": "真的么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "乱发头陀",
      "listener": "char_miao_wen",
      "text": "缪兄弟可在这里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "乱发头陀",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好极好极，果然全在这里。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "乱发头陀",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "你……你……可是……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_wen",
      "speaker_name": "缪文",
      "listener": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "此人可就是大师所要寻找之人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "乱发头陀",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "你……你转过脸来，让我看上一眼。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "乱发头陀",
      "listener": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "text": "你要作甚？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "speaker_name": "华山银鹤",
      "listener": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "text": "岂有此理！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "speaker_name": "蒙面老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们可是要我转身么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luan_fa_tou_tuo",
      "speaker_name": "乱发头陀",
      "listener": "char_hu_zhi_hui",
      "text": "请……让……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    }
  ],
